title: The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but it changes with settings
OB: When clicking on the "OK" button and then reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes "www.actuate.com".
EB: The expected result is that the hyperlink builder title should be "Hyperlink Options".
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the hyperlink builder.
2. Click on the "OK" button.
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
